<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hey" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hey,</orth> 1) a cry to set dogs on: <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.256" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 256</bibl>. 2) a frolicking exclamation: <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 3, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 3, 18</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tn 4.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. IV, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.399.78" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 399</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 3.2.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 2, 75</bibl> (Ff <emph>heigh-ho</emph>). <cit><quote>h. nonny,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.3.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 3, 71</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a h. nonino,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 3, 18</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>h. non nonny, nonny, h. nonny,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 165</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>